{"tid":2423623,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟曾經做嘢好忙，淪落到要搵機會去屙屎？","createTime":"2021-02-26T04:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T04:21:53.000Z","uid":40930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57b964d38e862ad180874c732cec13ad2238b744","tid":2423623,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"返工簽嗰份垃圾約都唔會專登講你每日幾點鐘去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上屙屎係人類本能，返工去屙屎根本談不上要就咩schedule 啊 、就meeting 之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你想幾時屙、屙幾耐、屙幾多舊、諗住邊位同事去屙等等都應該係你嘅自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼見好多人就係忘記咗本能法則，以遷就工作而非遷就屙屎嚟去返工，呢樣簡直係人性淪喪，係一場生態災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見過一位舊同事曾經洋洋自得咁同人講：「我今日涉到時間去屙屎啊、嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n佢真係痴撚咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返工屙屎要睇自己得唔得閒？What? <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}